medieq.iet.model
Interface Document

All Known Implementing Classes:
DocumentImpl
public interface Document

Document representation used within IET. IET may use the getClassifications() method to decide which extraction models it will apply to the Document. Using applicable models, IET adds to the Document's metadata extracted attribute values and also instances composed of these attribute values. IET can also annotate the document content with colored labels which represent attribute values (or their alternative versions). Tables can be added to the content which represent extracted instances.
